# Cashier UI & Screen Design — Implementation Guide

## Overview

This document translates the `docs/09-ui/05-cashier.md` UX architecture into detailed screen designs with API endpoints, component hierarchy, and interaction patterns optimized for lunch-rush speed.

**Design Philosophy:** Every click costs time. Minimize clicks. Maximize defaults. The default quantity is 1. The default payment method is Cash. The default action after adding an item is staying in the menu to add more.

