## Screen 2: Order Panel

### Layout
```text
┌──────────────────────────────────────┐
│ [✕] Table: T1   #1024  Draft        │
├──────────────────────────────────────┤
│ Item              Qty     Price      │
│ Chicken Rice      2       90.00     │
│   [-] 2 [+] [×]                     │
│ Water             2       20.00     │
│   [-] 2 [+] [×]                     │
│                          ──────     │
│ Total                   110.00     │
├──────────────────────────────────────┤
│ [+ Add Item]  [✓ Confirm]  [✗ Cancel]│
│ [Process Payment]  [Print Receipt]   │
└──────────────────────────────────────┘
```

| Property | Value |
|----------|-------|
| **API** | `GET /orders/{id}`, `POST .../items`, `DELETE .../items/{id}`, `POST .../confirm`, `POST .../cancel` |
| **Shortcuts** | `Ctrl+N` add, `Ctrl+Enter` confirm, `Ctrl+P` payment, `Escape` close |
| **States** | Loading, Empty (no items), Draft (editable), Confirmed (view-only), Completed (disabled) |
| **Touch** | 44×44px qty buttons, full-width action buttons |

Quantity controls inline — no detail dialog needed. Total updates instantly.

